title: Zippered propane tank sleeve

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a zippered propane tank sleeve, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a top plan view of a zippered propane tank sleeve according to my design;
FIG. 2 is a plan view thereof; and,
FIG. 3 is a view of a bottom plan view of a zippered propane tank sleeve as illustrated in FIGS. 1 and 2, according to my new design.
The broken line showing is included for the purpose of illustrating environment and forms no part of the claimed design.
